room_title: Escape room "Ice Station Zero" by Mass Escape in New Bedford
room_description: It’s the height of the Cold War and your highly skilled and secret team is being sent on an urgent mission.  We have lost all contact with one of our isolated nuclear launch centers located deep in the Arctic. You’ve got a short time window to get in, find out what happened and if necessary recover all the top-secret materials and initiate the self-destruct sequence!
